title.9: Darkhold: Pages from the Book of Sins (1992) #10
title.50: Darkhold: Pages from the Book of Sins (1992) #9

description.7: The rage of ROADKILL! The wrathful spirit is out for revenge, and he'll get it even if that means going straight through Namorita! But he'll also have to face off with another man who knows a thing or two about revenge, as the Punisher comes bearing down on Roadkill's rampage!
description.8: Rage seeks out gang member Kimeiko Ashu in the name of his family!
description.19: The Avengers West Coast joined by Darkhawk look to stave off the Pacific Overlords, but what deadly secret does Dr. Demonicus hold?
description.24: The aptly-named Stilt-Man makes life harder for Daredevil! Featuring the Wildboys and Taskmaster too!
description.25: Captain America shows up to take Marlo Chandler into his custody, but a big green wall stands in his way! The Hulk and the leader of the Avengers brawl for the fate of Rick Jones' love!
description.26: Iron Man battles berserkers and countless mind-slaves! But wait until you meet their boss-the Controller! As you've never before seen him!
description.28: The Freakers are just another group of baddies creating chaos on the streets of New York. But how are these thugs more dangerous than the Public Eye? And how can Spider-Man get involved without civilian casualties?
description.29: A love triangle boils over between Thor, Dark Valkyrie, and the Goddess!
description.32: The young Franklin Richards returns as a teenager, having spent years fighting in a war of the future! What plan does he have for the present day? And will the FF be able to figure it out before they're taken out by the deadly new villain squad known as the Fearsome Foursome!?
description.33: The claws are out! Wolverine, Jubilee, and Rogue split up and have to fend for themselves in the Savage Land. In the midst of a fight with Sauron, Wolverine loses his temper… badly.
description.42: The Avengers track down the Gatherers and their leader Proctor, but why he is blaming Sersei for the destruction of parralel Earths? And what causes the Black Knight to turn on his teammates?
description.44: Captain America is surrounded by A.I.M. agents and Dino-Men! Can the Star-Spangled Avenger fight his way out of the Savage Lands? He's faced worse, right?
description.48: Who is Harlan Silverbird and what nefarious scheme does he have regarding outer space?
description.53: Once, Patsy Walker AKA Hellcat was Daimon Hellstrom's happy bride. But that all changed with a stroke of bad, poisoned luck. The love story of Daimon and Patsy recounted in full.
description.54: Brutal murders of the homeless have set Spider-Man and The Punisher on a mission to find the cause. The unlikely allies have a suspect in their sights?Sabretooth! Are they senseless murders, or is there something WORSE beneath the surface?
description.61: A new arc means a NEW SECRET DEFENDERS TEAM! Doctor Strange has sent out the call, and Sleepwalker and Namorita have answered! But they're not the only ones - they'll be joined by none other than Frank Castle, the PUNISHER!
description.67: War Machine joins as the newest member of the Avengers West Coast. And they'll need every bit of his firepower to take on the Pacific Overlords.
description.69: After freeing Morbius’ body, Nightmare crosses the threshold of our dimension through Doc's body!
description.72: Matt Murdock goes “underground” in one dustup of an issue!
description.74: Hulk's in the middle of a dangerous love triangle! When Ajax sees Achilles with Atalanta, you'd think Ajax's the one with the anger problem! Hulk must intervene before property damage, and broken hearts, ensue.
description.75: Once news breaks out that Tony Stark is alive and well, and is beginning his recuperation in physical therapy, he is attacked by a Berserker. Could this mean the Controller has returned to finish Tony Stark off?
description.78: Spider-Man continues to have a turf battle with an impressive incarnation of the Vulture. And Vulture 2099 may have some surprising tech up his wing. Miguel may have to rely on his past as an engineer to outwit this tech-savvy foe.
description.79: Pluto capitalizes on Thor's vulnerable state, making a final bid against the mighty Thunderer!
description.82: Having barely survived their battle with Doom, the Fantastic Four have no time to rest as they're pulled into a battle for the future of everything! Leading the charge is none other than Reed's father Nathaniel Richards, as well as...an adult Franklin!?
description.83: The search for Magneto is ON and Wolverine, Jubilee, and Rogue are on the case.
description.84: Harry Osborn is starting to crack, and continues his homicidal rampage against Spider-Man. Mary Jane arrives in the nick of time with a saving grace.
description.88: Spider-Man continues to duke it out with Styx and Stone, but Cardiac has a more direct means to an end. Will Spidey end up a victim in Cardiac's master plan?
description.89: The alternate dimension Vision is able to seriously injure the Swordsman, which leads the Avengers to vow to take the fight to the Gatherers.
description.90: It's jungle mayhem as the Black Panther takes on Kazar! Will our heroes set aside their difference long enough to stop A.I.M. from destroying the jungle?
description.94: At the mercy of MACABRE! Wolverine, Spider-Woman, and Nomad are held captive by the sinister sorceress, and only a considerably weakened Doctor Strange can save them!
description.98: Marc Spector makes a life-altering decision.  Moon Knight is an Avenger no longer!

3.text: Infinity Crusade crossover! Dormammu tries to persuade Doctor Strange to be his channel into another dimension, because the Dread One is so afraid of The Goddess!

5.text: Rancor sets out to avenge her ancestor Wolverine!

6.text: The Carnal Serpent awakens! Silver Sable, Terror and Cage do unholy battle.

7.text: The rage of ROADKILL! The wrathful spirit is out for revenge, and he'll get it even if that means going straight through Namorita! But he'll also have to face off with another man who knows a thing or two about revenge, as the Punisher comes bearing down on Roadkill's rampage!

9.text: Jinx shows that he can pull his weight when he rescues the entire team from death! Who is Diabolique?

10.text: U.S. Agent must go undercover and infiltrate a secret organization that is rumored to produce mass murderers!

11.text: Calypso, Zombie and a possession mean the supernatural has come for Daredevil.

13.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 4 As the battle between good and evil heats up, strange alliances are formed. Can a partnership between Venom and Spider-Man remain stable long enough to take Carnage down?

14.text: Multiple Man locates Mutate 24601 while X-Factor battles it out with the Magistrates.

16.text: A Tale of Two Psylockes! The team meets the Silver Samurai in Japan!

17.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 3 Venom and Spider-Man are on the hunt for Carnage on the streets of New York!

18.text: The Goddess has half of the Marvel Universe on her side, but if she doesn't get her way, she's ready to destroy all of it!
The Goddess has half of the Marvel Universe on her side, but if she doesn't get her way, she's ready to destroy all of it!

19.text: The Avengers West Coast joined by Darkhawk look to stave off the Pacific Overlords, but what deadly secret does Dr. Demonicus hold?

20.text: IT'S ALL ABOUT SURVIVAL! Cyclops, Storm, and Prof. X are trapped in the Antartic by Siena Blaze in a plot to kill them in the Upstart's game.

21.text: Eternity’s prophecy comes to fruition at Monster Isle. Who is Maxam? Can he be the ‘One entangled in a Web of Past and Future Woes’? Given his amnesia and violent rage towards Warlock, Maxam fits the bill!

23.text: Back to the future! Excalibur finds themselves in the year 2015 fighting alongside the future R.C.X. against a new leader- Ahab and his Hounds!

30.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 2 Spider-Man, Cloak, and Dagger face off against the deranged Doppelganger!

36.text: Sluggo and Deadpool are beat to the punch at Vanessa's place, when Domino arrives to confront Copycat! Cannonball revokes his promise to Professor X.

40.text: Strange recruits Eternity’s help and defeats their champion to gain secret knowledge into the events of the Infinity Crusade!

43.text: Cable has made it to the past. But not all is as it seems...
Cable has made it to the past. But not all is as it seems...

45.text: Does everyone really hate Fight Man? Comic book legend Evan Dorkin brings you the off-beat hero that can’t seem to stay out of trouble!

47.text: Following the frightening threat of the Night Beast, Luke and inadvertent stowaway Threepio travel to the desert world of Aridus to ensure the continuation of the Rebel Alliance's weapons-smuggling operation. But Luke is more interested in checking out rumors of a mysterious stranger who's appeared on Aridus claiming to be Ben Kenobi!

49.text: Namorita makes a costly mistake that puts the Warriors in danger.

50.text: Sam Buchanan may not be aligned with the Redeemers after all. Jinx, the grandson of Louise Hastings, lends his expertise of the occult to Vicki’s cause.

51.text: Johnny Walker is the world’s last hope of defeating the super-villain mass-murderer, Scourge.

54.text: Brutal murders of the homeless have set Spider-Man and The Punisher on a mission to find the cause. The unlikely allies have a suspect in their sights…Sabretooth! Are they senseless murders, or is there something WORSE beneath the surface?

55.text: Cable is on a mission and nothing will get in his way!

57.text: Adam Warlock vs. Mephisto in a battle of cosmic illusions! Silver Surfer and the Infinity Watch can only observe the showdown for the soul of Shalla-Bal. Mephisto proves a sore loser. Norrin and Shalla-Bal are reunited once more- but for how long?

58.text: Eric Masterson takes up his mantle as Thunderstrike in the wake of a violent crime wave!

59.text: Dormammu has claimed the immortal soul of the dead Doctor Strange!

60.text: Silver Sable and Terror guest-star! Cage joins the mercenaries-for-hire to maintain an ancient talisman.

61.text: A new arc means a NEW SECRET DEFENDERS TEAM! Doctor Strange has sent out the call, and Sleepwalker and Namorita have answered! But they're not the only ones - they'll be joined by none other than Frank Castle, the PUNISHER!

62.text: Who is X-Cutioner? And what does Mastermind want with Jean Grey?

63.text: Cable must return to the past. But what deadly path must be trave to claim the Temporal Device known as...The Timex!
Cable must return to the past. But what deadly path must be trave to claim the Temporal Device known as...The Timex!

64.text: Havok, Strong Guy, and Multiple Man battle the Genoshan president’s bodyguard, Mutate 416. The team tries to get to the disease-ridden Mutate 24601 before the Magistrates do.

66.text: Psylocke reveals that she's an impostor! How did Jean get her to confess?

67.text: War Machine joins as the newest member of the Avengers West Coast. And they'll need every bit of his firepower to take on the Pacific Overlords.

68.text: Warlock vs. the demons of Count Abyss! But what is the Count’s end goal? It’s a battle for the soul, as ‘One Being in need of a Soul’ emerges!

69.text: After freeing Morbius’ body, Nightmare crosses the threshold of our dimension through Doc's body!

73.text: Rachel, who is no longer possessed by the Phoenix Force, reveals her latest plan...

80.text: Spider-Man takes some new threads out for a spin in a giant-sized 100th issue!

85.text: Terrax the Tamer vs. Morg the Executioner: who will be victorious?

87.text: Final Retribution! Nick Fury goes all in for an epic battle between Gideon and Crule!

91.text: Silver Surfer and the Infinity Watch enter the hellish realm of Mephisto! In order to recover Shalla-Bal’s soul, Surfer gives Mephisto an ultimatum- his soul in exchange for his lover’s. Is this a Faustian deal too good to refuse? Adam Warlock holds the upper hand when he claims to have the Soul Gem.

92.text: The Galactic Guardians, the Guardians of the Galaxy, and Krugarr all team up to battle Dormammu!

93.text: The Tinkerer’s son is now safe thanks to Cage and Dakota North. But can the same be said for Coldfire, Luke’s recently transformed brother?

94.text: At the mercy of MACABRE! Wolverine, Spider-Woman, and Nomad are held captive by the sinister sorceress, and only a considerably weakened Doctor Strange can save them!

95.text: Captain America, Namor, the Human Torch, and the Liberty Legion take on the Battle-Axis.

96.text: Leia, Luke, Han, and Chewie finally make it back to Rebel headquarters in the Yavin system only to find it under attack by Imperial forces! With the Millennium Falcon's help, the Rebels emerge victorious. But even as they celebrate, the battle sparks some unexpected results in the form of an ancient threat that lurks within the very heart of Yavin's moon!

97.text: Heroes die as the global war continues!

99.text: Cardinal returns and he's not alone! Are the New Warriors ready to handle the high-flying attack of Air Force?
